name: #01 - bulbasur - pokmopxlnft
description: In the Pokémon franchise, BulbasaurPXL are small, squat amphibian and plant Pokémon that move on all four legs, and have light blue-green bodies with darker blue-green spots. As a BulbasaurPXL undergoes evolution into IvysaurPX and then later into VenusaurPXL, the bulb on its back blossoms into a large flower.
